item.title: Im back yo
item.dc:creator: @oldschool-scape oldschool-scape
item.description:
@oldschool-scape wrote:

TabbyKiller:

Something deeply terrible happened after you left, something we must not ever speak of again, but as you can see from the previous comments above, everybody has gone full retard. The people you see here now ate everyone you knew and came to love. Though there are a few survivors out there like I who have been surviving off the retarded post residue the infected leave behind, I fear if we continue to do so we will end up just like them. It’s been so long I cannot even remember what a half decent intelligent post looks like anymore. What is the day? Has Hanukkah passed? Did the Kardashians pay for a one way trip to Mars yet? Are you here to save us?

The Oblivion crisis is over now.
